    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Everything is gone. The market crash just wiped out everything we built over the last five years, and now the debt collectors are already calling. I can't even look my parents in the eye. I feel like such a joke. There’s no way to fix this, there is no path back from this kind of failure.",
